							<p>Boba tea, also known as bubble tea, is a delightful drink that has taken the world by storm. Originating from Taiwan, this unique beverage combines tea, milk, and chewy tapioca pearls, creating a one-of-a-kind drinking experience. Whether you're new to boba tea or looking to learn more about it, this beginner's guide will cover everything you need to know.</p>

